{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"2275b","heading":"Requirements for appropriate classification guidance","label":"2275b Requirements for appropriate classification guidance","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptIV/ch135","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2275b","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Amendments2024— struck out period at end of section catchline.Pub. L. 118–159"],"amendments":["Amendments2024— struck out period at end of section catchline.Pub. L. 118–159"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—In General","label":"a .—In General","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2275b%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2275b%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"if such guidance is determined to be appropriate, submit to the congressional defense committees a certification of such determination; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2275b%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"if such guidance is determined to be inappropriate, initiate an update to such guidance.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Definitions","label":"b .—Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2275b%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2275b%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “Milestone B approval” has the meaning given such term in .section 4172(e)(7) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2275b%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “major defense acquisition program” has the meaning given such term in .section 4201 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2275b/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs2275b%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “space major defense acquisition program” means a major defense acquisition program for the acquisition of a satellite, ground system, or command and control system.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
